# AggregationType

Counter aggregation type. Can be `Sum`, `Average`, `Min`, `Max` or `Percent`

**Properties**

| Name    | Type | Required | Description |
| :------ | :--- | :------- | :---------- |
| SUM     | str  | ✅       | "Sum"       |
| AVERAGE | str  | ✅       | "Average"   |
| MAX     | str  | ✅       | "Max"       |
| MIN     | str  | ✅       | "Min"       |
| PERCENT | str  | ✅       | "Percent"   |
